entry.title: Godedupe
entry.content: Project URL: github.com/OSPG/godedupe Language: Go Summary: An utility to find duplicated files. Godedupe finds duplicated files like fdupes does. Unlike fdupes, we focus on speed and features.

entry.title: Contact Us
entry.content: If you have any questions regarding this site or the organization you can open an issue on https://github.com/OSPG/ospg.github.io. For more informal questions there is an IRC server at mumei.
